Whenever the project needs to be built, either use the VS Code task "build" or run this command:
"cd flutter_secure_storage_devtool_extension_web && dart run devtools_extensions build_and_copy --source=. --dest=../flutter_secure_storage_devtool/extension/devtools && cd .."

When project version should be increased, do the following:

run "dart update_version.dart <version>" where <version> should be replaced by the specific version

Update the changelog, and if the changes contains new features then add them to the readme.

Run the VS Code script "build" or the command "cd flutter_secure_storage_devtool_extension_web && dart run devtools_extensions build_and_copy --source=. --dest=../flutter_secure_storage_devtool/extension/devtools && cd .."

Finally run the VS Code script "publish" or the command "cd flutter_secure_storage_devtool && dart pub publish && cd .."
